column1: Baby Barnaby's////There's honestly not a whole lot to add here. Really delicious brunch
column2: and the biscuits were surprisingly good. The green eggs and ham were an awesome order
column3: and I'll probably get them again. The line can get long
column4: so I'd recommend coming here earlier. When you get here
column5: just put your name on the legal pad they have hanging. I'm also not sure why this Barnaby's Cafe is so much more popular than the others
column6: but I guess I'll have to try the other ones too!
